Two game-action and one post game cabinet cards.  These three blank-backed cabinet cards show great detail of the early game.  They came from a period photo album of cabinet cards from the New England area.  $(Sold)delivered (MO, check or Paypal f/f).  Thanks for looking.  Rob M
